<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="23Jun1904"><font color="red">23 June 1904</font>, <cite>Selected Letters</cite> 22 (JJ to C.P. Curran): Dublin. <br>Here is the marvellous novel [possibly Chapters I-X] delivered to you by my twenty-third sister. [&hellip;] If you are too busy to read the novel now, no harm. But as soon as you have read it send me word to meet you on some altitude where we can utter our souls unmolested. [&hellip;] Yours heroically. Stephen Daedalus</div>
